
  CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ODS_T_AAA_FILE 
   (
	AAA01 VARCHAR(5) NOT NULL,

	AAA02 VARCHAR(80), 
	AAA03 VARCHAR(4), 
	AAA04 INT, 
	AAA05 INT, 
	AAA06 DATE, 
	AAA07 DATE, 
	AAA08 INT, 
	AAAACTI VARCHAR(1), 
	AAAUSER VARCHAR(10), 
	AAAGRUP VARCHAR(10), 
	AAAMODU VARCHAR(10), 
	AAADATE DATE, 
	AAA09 VARCHAR(1), 
	AAA10 VARCHAR(1), 
	AAAORIU VARCHAR(10), 
	AAAORIG VARCHAR(10), 
	AAA11 VARCHAR(24), 
	AAA12 VARCHAR(24), 
	AAA14 VARCHAR(24), 
	AAA15 VARCHAR(24), 
	AAA16 VARCHAR(24), 
	AAA13 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	AAA17 VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	TA_AAA01 VARCHAR(10), 
	TA_AAA02 VARCHAR(1), 
	TA_AAA03 VARCHAR(1), 
	TA_AAA04 DATE, 
	TA_AAA05 INT, 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(AAA01)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(AAA01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

-- Converted from Oracle table: AAA_FILE


  CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ODS_T_AAB_FILE 
   (

	AAB03 VARCHAR(255),

        modtime DATETIME
)

    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	APX01 VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
	APX02 INT NOT NULL,
	APXLEGAL VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,


	APX03 VARCHAR(20), 
	APX04F DECIMAL(20,6) NOT NULL,
	APX04 DECIMAL(20,6) NOT NULL,

 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(APX01, APX02, APXLEGAL)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(APX01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	ASW01 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW02 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW03 VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	ASW031 VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	ASW04 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW11 VARCHAR(4)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	ASWLEGAL VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',





	ASW05 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	ASW06 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	ASW07 VARCHAR(10), 
	ASW08 VARCHAR(10), 
	ASW09 VARCHAR(24), 
	ASW10 VARCHAR(24), 

	ASW12 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW13 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW131 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW14 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW15 DECIMAL(15,3)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW16 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	ASW17 VARCHAR(20), 
	ASW18 VARCHAR(20), 
	ASW19 VARCHAR(24), 

 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(ASW01, ASW02, ASW03, ASW031, ASW04, ASW11, ASWLEGAL)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(ASW01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)

	CDH01 VARCHAR(5)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	CDH02 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH03 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH04 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	CDH05 VARCHAR(40)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	CDH06 VARCHAR(40)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	CDH07 VARCHAR(40)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	CDHLEGAL VARCHAR(10), 







	CDH08 VARCHAR(24) DEFAULT ' ',
	CDH09 DECIMAL(15,3)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10 DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10A DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10B DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10C DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10D DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10E DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10F DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10G DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH10H DECIMAL(20,6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	CDH11 VARCHAR(10), 

	CDHORIG VARCHAR(10), 
	CDHORIU VARCHAR(10), 
	CDHPLANT VARCHAR(10), 

 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(CDH00, CDH01, CDH02, CDH03, CDH04, CDH05, CDH06, CDH07, CDHLEGAL)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(CDH00) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	CNF01 VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
	CNF02 VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL,
	CNF03 DATE NOT NULL,
	CNFLEGAL VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,



	CNF04 INT, 
	CNF05 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF06 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF07 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF08 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF09 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF10 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF11 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF12 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF13 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF14 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF15 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF16 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF17 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF18 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF19 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNF20 DECIMAL(15,3), 
	CNFPLANT VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,

 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(CNF01, CNF02, CNF03, CNFLEGAL)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(CNF01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

        validity INT,

    "replication_num" = "2"

	GSF01 VARCHAR(6) NOT NULL,

	GSF02 VARCHAR(80), 
	GSF03 VARCHAR(1), 
	GSF04 VARCHAR(24), 
	GSF05 VARCHAR(1), 
	GSF06 VARCHAR(1), 
	GSFACTI VARCHAR(1), 
	GSFUSER VARCHAR(10), 
	GSFGRUP VARCHAR(10), 
	GSFMODU VARCHAR(10), 
	GSFDATE DATE, 
	GSF041 VARCHAR(24), 
	GSFORIG VARCHAR(10), 
	GSFORIU VARCHAR(10), 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(GSF01)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(GSF01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	MBI01 VARCHAR(6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBI00 VARCHAR(5), 

	MBI02 VARCHAR(80), 
	MBI03 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBIACTI VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBIDATE DATE, 
	MBIGRUP VARCHAR(10), 
	MBIMODU VARCHAR(10), 
	MBIORIG VARCHAR(10), 
	MBIORIU VARCHAR(10), 
	MBIUSER VARCHAR(10), 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(MBI01)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(MBI01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

-- Converted from Oracle table: MBI_FILE


  CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ODS_T_MBJ_FILE 
   (
	MBJ01 VARCHAR(6)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ02 DECIMAL(9,4)  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',


	MBJ03 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ04 INT, 
	MBJ05 INT, 
	MBJ06 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ07 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ08 INT, 
	MBJ09 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ11 VARCHAR(1)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	MBJ20 VARCHAR(255), 
	MBJ20E VARCHAR(80), 
	MBJ23 VARCHAR(2), 
	MBJ26 INT, 
	MBJ27 VARCHAR(256), 
	MBJ28 VARCHAR(256), 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(MBJ01, MBJ02)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(MBJ01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

-- Converted from Oracle table: MBJ_FILE

	SGYI02 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	SGYI03 INT  NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
	SGYI05 VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	SGYI012 VARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',
	SGYILEGAL VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,




	SGYISLK01 INT, 
	SGYISLK03 DECIMAL(8,4), 
	SGYISLK04 DECIMAL(20,6), 
	SGYISLK05 DECIMAL(20,6), 
	SGYISLK06 INT, 
	SGYISLK08 DECIMAL(8,4), 
	SGYISLK09 DECIMAL(20,6), 
	SGYISLK10 DECIMAL(20,6), 
	SGYIPLANT VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,


 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(SGYI01, SGYI02, SGYI03, SGYI05, SGYI012, SGYILEGAL)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(SGYI01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

-- Converted from Oracle table: SGYI_FILE


  CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ODS_T_SGY_FILE

        validity INT,

	SHAORIG VARCHAR(10), 

 
        validity INT,

)

DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(SHA01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	SKL03 VARCHAR(40)  NOT NULL DEFAULT ' ',

	SKLDATE DATE, 
	SKLGRUP VARCHAR(10), 
	SKLMODU VARCHAR(10), 
	SKLUSER VARCHAR(10), 
	SKLORIG VARCHAR(10), 
	SKLORIU VARCHAR(10), 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(SKL01, SKL03)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(SKL01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	TRX01 VARCHAR(6) NOT NULL,
	TRX02 VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,


	TRX03 VARCHAR(255), 
 
        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(TRX01, TRX02)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(TRX01) BUCKETS 10
PROPERTIES (
    "replication_num" = "2"
);

	VAS07 VARCHAR(60),

        validity INT,
        modtime DATETIME
)
UNIQUE KEY(VASLEGAL, VASPLANT, VAS01)

    "replication_num" = "2"
